               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡; Bandlet of Righteousness, The Prayer of the Blessed Virgin Mary at Golgotha, ጸሎተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘሰኔ፡ ጎልጎታ፡, and collection of fragments from various sources</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="7r" to="16r" facs="009">Fols 7r–16r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2444Temher">Tǝmhǝrta
                                                  ḫǝbuʾāt</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="16v" to="33v" facs="019">Fols 16v–33v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1758Lefafa">Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                    <locus from="37r" to="63r" facs="039">Fols 37r–63r</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2246salotz">Ṣalot za-ʾǝgzǝʾǝtǝna
                                                  Māryām ba-Dabra Golgotā</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                    <note>Copied and printed several times in its Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic versions</note>
                  </msItem>

